{"tid":132323,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[耳機撚] 討論下香港各大耳機店 (10)","createTime":"2017-02-23T17:33:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-23T17:52:38.000Z","uid":199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4b471930140d91902bf5417bbd82ff34fa8bbc47","tid":132323,"uid":199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T17:33:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">各位新黎既巴絲請詳細閱讀第一頁，以免問題不停回帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新黎既巴/絲打歡迎留一留低自己聽歌器材既資料(新link)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://docs.google.com/spreadsheet/viewform?formkey=dFFGTFdGV21nemQteldTaV83V1lKSlE6MQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheet%2Fviewform%3Fformkey%3DdFFGTFdGV21nemQteldTaV83V1lKSlE6MQ&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTeaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=1e5d95e8\" target=\"_blank\">http://docs.google.com/spreadsheet/viewform?formkey=dFFGTFdGV21nemQteldTaV83V1lKSlE6MQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢頁可以睇番其他巴打填左乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://docs.google.com/spreadsheet/ccc?key=0AsCwmQJKoVjPdFFGTFdGV21nemQteldTaV83V1lKSlE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheet%2Fccc%3Fkey%3D0AsCwmQJKoVjPdFFGTFdGV21nemQteldTaV83V1lKSlE&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTeaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=6ac942e1\" target=\"_blank\">http://docs.google.com/spreadsheet/ccc?key=0AsCwmQJKoVjPdFFGTFdGV21nemQteldTaV83V1lKSlE</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n舊Link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://tinyurl.com/eargay2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftinyurl.com%2Feargay2&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTeaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=e8967780\" target=\"_blank\">http://tinyurl.com/eargay2</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n耳機潮文合集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://docs.google.com/document/d/1Im5370mKsPKPZGJhqVGWocLcy5P22YHgdlnx5hmlx_k/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1Im5370mKsPKPZGJhqVGWocLcy5P22YHgdlnx5hmlx_k%2Fedit&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTeaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=e072aa92\" target=\"_blank\">http://docs.google.com/document/d/1Im5370mKsPKPZGJhqVGWocLcy5P22YHgdlnx5hmlx_k/edit</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n耳機推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://docs.google.com/document/d/1tMEkzWyPyuTw56QVJNdV8TIRk30M3w03RN4xEYWLkD8/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1tMEkzWyPyuTw56QVJNdV8TIRk30M3w03RN4xEYWLkD8%2Fedit&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTeaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=1a0ff939\" target=\"_blank\">http://docs.google.com/document/d/1tMEkzWyPyuTw56QVJNdV8TIRk30M3w03RN4xEYWLkD8/edit</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCM推介(有待修改)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ierm更已新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://docs.google.com/document/d/1FKYVT8FxSpocfPju5aFfPVWAUbryrv-eVKBRvItYKLM/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1FKYVT8FxSpocfPju5aFfPVWAUbryrv-eVKBRvItYKLM%2Fedit&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTeaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=ec3f1913\" target=\"_blank\">http://docs.google.com/document/d/1FKYVT8FxSpocfPju5aFfPVWAUbryrv-eVKBRvItYKLM/edit</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAmp推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://docs.google.com/document/d/17OY_8Vrf3tGrWj-sbKXFbKiMDmFgL6r-UFt4XQVCqUc/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F17OY_8Vrf3tGrWj-sbKXFbKiMDmFgL6r-UFt4XQVCqUc%2Fedit&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTeaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=3093f092\" target=\"_blank\">http://docs.google.com/document/d/17OY_8Vrf3tGrWj-sbKXFbKiMDmFgL6r-UFt4XQVCqUc/edit</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDIY AMP<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://docs.google.com/document/d/1bPwtk_hct0uIywm4Ty1ykZzxuUdOpZNygMHtIVQ6T7M/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1bPwtk_hct0uIywm4Ty1ykZzxuUdOpZNygMHtIVQ6T7M%2Fedit&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTeaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=72a38cac\" target=\"_blank\">http://docs.google.com/document/d/1bPwtk_hct0uIywm4Ty1ykZzxuUdOpZNygMHtIVQ6T7M/edit</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">FAQ：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Q1：</span>1000蚊之內budget買咩入耳式好？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">A1：</span>出旺角各大耳機鋪試下(唔試過點知邊隻最適合自己？)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">毒撚到冇朋友</span>巴打真心推介：hifiman re400，平衡度相當高，極之適合雜食。<br />\n<br />\n重Bass：se215(LE)、sony xb90ex (停左產難搵)<br />\n<br />\n人聲/平衡：mc5(難推)、fxd80(停左產難搵)、philips s2、heaven ii、ath-im50、ath-im70、sony xba-100、a1、jvc fxt208se，仲有對冇得試既apple earpod。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Q2：</span>耳機得番一邊有聲點搞？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">A2：</span>依個情況多數係條耳機線暗斷，仲有保養就拎上代理換。<br />\n<br />\n過左保可以上恆源/<span style=\"color: red;\">波sir(大伏，手功麻麻)/Hercules小修小寶工作室(服務同手功較好)</span>道整或者自已剪左個插頭焊過個新既。<br />\n<br />\n但未必一定成功<span style=\"color: red;\">(亦有可能中伏)</span>，<br />\n<br />\n亦可以考慮買過對新既耳機。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Q3：</span>耳棉或耳膠爛左去邊道買番黎換？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">A3：</span>基本上各大耳機店都有Comply棉賣(好易爛)，<br />\n<br />\n推介monster super tips，隔音唔錯之餘仲幾耐用。<br />\n<br />\n另外耳棉耳膠係旺角德發地庫都有得賣(三節膠最隔音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，<br />\n<br />\n大約$40-$50一對。"},{"pid":"27d1f7c666ea49b23e958ecdfbe41306d1f03925","tid":132323,"uid":199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T17:33:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">亦軒耳機音樂世界</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mingo-hmw.com/home/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingo-hmw.com%2Fhome%2F&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTeaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=7d7980b9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mingo-hmw.com/home/</a><br />\n<br />\nGOOD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多好多好多耳機免費任試，面皮夠厚既話，可試足一個下午<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 貨品種類繁多<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 分店多，地點便利<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 亦軒論壇個二手買賣區，間中會搵到筍野(<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你一定要知價，否則做水魚)<br />\n<br />\nBAD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 貨品價錢偏貴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，大部份貨品都賣貴過甚他鋪頭<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 開左鋪後，佢個論壇變了質，好多野都俾人大吹一餐，或人云亦云，D意見睇下就算，最緊要親自試聽<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人流多，唔少耳機都俾人試到殘晒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">金聲耳筒專門店</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.headphonehk.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.headphonehk.com%2F&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTeaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=bcfbba9c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.headphonehk.com/</a><br />\n<br />\nGOOD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔少耳機都可以任試 (但冇亦軒咁多)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 總店人流較少，環境靜D，可以專心D試耳機，耳機也比較新淨<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 分店多，地點尚算方便<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 價錢比亦軒平<br />\n<br />\nBAD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 買野前切記一定要問清楚是行定水貨、保養條款、檢查行貨包裝上有沒有香港代理的貼紙和標籤<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">AV2000</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.av2000.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.av2000.com.hk&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTeaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=959a1b18\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.av2000.com.hk</a><br />\n<br />\nGOOD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 價錢<span style=\"color: pink;\"><del>通常比其他鋪頭</del></span>平，會講明係行貨定水貨<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 據聞個老闆以前在某影音鋪打工，對影音產品既意見較專業<br />\n<br />\nBAD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 乜撚野都冇得試<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鋪頭細小，貨品款式不及亦軒、金聲咁多，更沒有售賣大陸牌子耳機，以大牌子的熱門貨品為主<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">DMA 泛音</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.dma-audio.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dma-audio.com%2F&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTeaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=1a9ea9ca\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.dma-audio.com/</a><br />\n<br />\nGOOD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多高檔野試<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有D牌子都做返街價<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有出自己牌子既HP架，都有ATH架<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有SOUND CARD，DAC，AMP，喇叭，DAP賣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 牌子相對比較齊<br />\n<br />\nBAD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 某D牌子仍屬於貴<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢賣既多數都係高檔貨，小朋友玩唔起，得個睇字 (依家其實都有唔少入門野賣)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <del>冇DENON</del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26172a8962c23f97e88c037bced64e01b2f11d41","tid":132323,"uid":199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T17:33:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>Jaben HK</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.jaben.com.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jaben.com.hk%2F&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTeaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=3646dd5b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.jaben.com.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\nGOOD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多貴野試，做cm可以即場做埋耳印<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁多間入面試耳機最好環境，閒日時間少人夠晒靜，任試唔嬲<br />\n<br />\nBAD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比較貴，視姦play<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">恆源</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://fs-digital.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs-digital.net%2F&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTeaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=a05475c5\" target=\"_blank\">http://fs-digital.net/</a><br />\n<br />\nGOOD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有自家品牌，地方比較靜<br />\n<br />\nBAD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> D產品都係戇鳩調音，乜都賣得貴過人，馬撚又小器又封閉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>天下影音：(16/F)</strong></span> </span><br />\n<br />\nGOOD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有D貨會劈價<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係比較有名氣牌子 (唔會有大陸牌子)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 賣HI-FI種類多，有興趣巴打可以順便望望<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 行內消息：由Denon代理開既 (好難証實，但有Denon野賣，DMA係冇Denon野)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有分店，但System及貨量都係獨立，所以佢既分店呢間冇可以走去第間睇睇或者格價<br />\n<br />\nBAD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 試既多數係HP<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有平野賣，但唔多<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要格價(拿，唔好話我唔提)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 限定版唔洗諗，應該好難會入到手<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 行內消息：T字頭代理會唔派貨，正如AX2XXX咁 (原因都係個價做壞市)，換句話講唔一定有HIT既貨品<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似冇MONSTER貨<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>華仁：(10/F)</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\nGOOD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 價錢都肯追貼街價<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 環境好 (但唔太靜，如果有人試HI-FI)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有HI-FI野睇同小量DAC/AMP野<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有BD賣 (價錢唔好諗佢平)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 店員幾NICE (第一次上去果時，第二次就差D笑容，但佢都樂意拎俾你聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 旗艦級IEM都有得試，etc. IE8、SE535<br />\n<br />\nBAD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 牌子小 只有ATH SEN記 加MONSTER同SHURE<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 價錢唔好最平<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 主打HI-FI 所以唔好望D野好齊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 容納人數小，試聽頂多4、5人已經叫FULL<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">英京：(8/F</span>)</strong></span><br />\n<br />\nGOOD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同天下(16/F)差唔多<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 感覺AMP/DAC種類較多(對比16/F)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 試耳機服務好過(16/F)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可訂貨<br />\n<br />\nBAD <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同天下(16/F)差唔多<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢地唔太SURE停產與否，都會叫你訂貨，例如W1000 (某D對呢方面唔太熟既職員會咁做)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">國際影音：(7/F</span>)</strong></span><br />\n<br />\nGOOD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 毒男O岩，望價睇野，佢都唔點理你<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 價錢都同友誠上下撞<br />\n<br />\nBAD <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 牌子小<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔太多耳機選擇"},{"pid":"ea71a28985a30568c66456dc2870337f6a521f0d","tid":132323,"uid":199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T17:34:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>耳機規格分析</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>頻率</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n單位為Hz<br />\n<br />\n當前數值越低，低音下潛力越高。(低音可以越低)<br />\n當後數值越高，高音上潛力越高。(高音可以越高)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>阻抗</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n單位為&Omega;(Ohm)<br />\n<br />\n當耳機的阻抗越高，<br />\n耳機需要的電流或電壓越大，<br />\n<strong>但阻抗與難推與否並非直接有關。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>靈敏度</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n單位為分貝(dB)<br />\n<br />\n指在1kHz頻率下，向耳機輸入1mW或1V的功率時，<br />\n耳機所能發出的聲壓級。<br />\n現時的入耳式耳筒都是105dB/mW以上。<br />\n耳機靈敏度越高，阻抗越少，耳機越易出聲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBy Berryz巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4db1d545f37a39519027ed080aaf41d111012481","tid":132323,"uid":199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T17:34:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>單元類別</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>動圈單元</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n現時大部分耳機 (無論入耳式或是頭戴式)，主要都是使用動圈單元。<br />\n發聲的原理和一般音箱一樣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i33.photobucket.com/albums/d67/omaeto/speaker_works.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi33.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fd67%2Fomaeto%2Fspeaker_works.jpg&h=bccc7401&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n例：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Sennheiser IE8</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.head-fi.org/1/10/800x600px-LL-10f7bf59_IE8-xlarge.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.head-fi.org%2F1%2F10%2F800x600px-LL-10f7bf59_IE8-xlarge.jpg&h=55b36d41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">HD800</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://zh-hk.sennheiser.com/images/718/all/square/5564/square_list_zoom_hd_800_silver_01_sq_sennheiser.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzh-hk.sennheiser.com%2Fimages%2F718%2Fall%2Fsquare%2F5564%2Fsquare_list_zoom_hd_800_silver_01_sq_sennheiser.png&h=f29a9e32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>動鐵式</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n又稱平衡電樞式。利用了電磁鐵產生交變磁場，振動部分是一個鐵片懸浮在電磁鐵前方。<br />\n當信號經過電磁鐵的時候會使電磁鐵磁場變化，從而使鐵片振動發聲。<br />\n優點是使用壽命長、效率高。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://diyaudioheaven.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/ba-driver.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdiyaudioheaven.files.wordpress.com%2F2013%2F05%2Fba-driver.png&h=3eec8d30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於動鐵單元細小，所以有很多入耳式耳筒安裝2-20個動鐵單元，分別用來分析高、中、低音。<br />\n <br />\n例：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Shure SE535</span> (三個動鐵單元，低頻*2，中高頻*1)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.shure.com.cn/dmsfiles/product_page_image_h/shure/products/earphones/images/se535/SE535_1-96e06f0a664f4d9debc3a5fa3ef3279c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.shure.com.cn%2Fdmsfiles%2Fproduct_page_image_h%2Fshure%2Fproducts%2Fearphones%2Fimages%2Fse535%2FSE535_1-96e06f0a664f4d9debc3a5fa3ef3279c.jpg&h=1ff818ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.shure.eu/dms/shure/products/earphones/images/se535/se535_en_internal_components_10_cols/se535_en_internal_components_10_cols.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.shure.eu%2Fdms%2Fshure%2Fproducts%2Fearphones%2Fimages%2Fse535%2Fse535_en_internal_components_10_cols%2Fse535_en_internal_components_10_cols.jpg&h=dfd0bb5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">JHAudio JH16Pro</span>(需要訂造耳模，八個動鐵單元，低頻*4、中頻*2、高頻*2)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.head-fi.org/8/8c/8c182a0f_img7553r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.head-fi.org%2F8%2F8c%2F8c182a0f_img7553r.jpg&h=1833bf10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">20單</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.barks.jp/image/review/1000076666/012.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.barks.jp%2Fimage%2Freview%2F1000076666%2F012.jpg&h=f10a5dab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">圈鐵混合</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同時採用動圈動鐵的單元，理論上能夠互補長短。<br />\n<br />\n例：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">AKG K3003</span> (一圈二鐵)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.lyra-media.com/ufiles/akg0729_k3003.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lyra-media.com%2Fufiles%2Fakg0729_k3003.jpg&h=35339a1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://isite.tw/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/K3003.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fisite.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F04%2FK3003.jpg&h=f9321730&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ce536e9b2bc5d178d454ce81333b351fa07e6fb0","tid":132323,"uid":199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T17:35:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>靜電單元</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n又稱為靜電平面振膜，是將導電體（一般為鋁）線圈直接電鍍或印刷在很薄的塑料膜上，精確到幾微米級。<br />\n將其置於強靜電場中，信號通過線圈的時候切割電場，帶動振膜振動發聲。<br />\n優點是線性好、失真小，高頻及瞬態反應快。<br />\n缺點是需要專門的驅動電路和靜電發生器、低頻反應差、價格昂貴、效率也不高。<br />\n<br />\n例：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">STAX SR-009</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.headamp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/SR009.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.headamp.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F06%2FSR009.jpg&h=a957018c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">ERGO A.M.T</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.precide.ch/pergo/new_ergoamp_kh1.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.precide.ch%2Fpergo%2Fnew_ergoamp_kh1.JPG&h=31d8248e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">AKG K1000</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.head-fi.org/e/e6/1000x500px-LL-e6f2bdf5_K1000.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.head-fi.org%2Fe%2Fe6%2F1000x500px-LL-e6f2bdf5_K1000.jpg&h=19aae404&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">代宣傳：高登耳機line群，入群者請填form，並在post內留言作實</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://goo.gl/forms/1HqFlp5weV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2F1HqFlp5weV&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTeaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=7fab74f7\" target=\"_blank\">http://goo.gl/forms/1HqFlp5weV</a></strong>"},{"pid":"aa95378b52fcdda549a8f95c04c6df63aedb5adc","tid":132323,"uid":199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T17:37:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0875/3864/products/Nova-Anodized-Beveled-Screw.jpg?v=1484531929\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.shopify.com%2Fs%2Ffiles%2F1%2F0875%2F3864%2Fproducts%2FNova-Anodized-Beveled-Screw.jpg%3Fv%3D1484531929&h=e8f25e2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港最平係咪要近$4000<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10a2c95dd7dcbe8bfd6b6f169fda532fb63d2feb","tid":132323,"uid":40751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T17:42:38.000Z","msg":"想問下巴打們點睇marshall major2? 是咪垃圾黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"756569638e8998c362ce790299ed272b2e6e21fe","tid":132323,"uid":199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T17:52:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下巴打們點睇marshall major2? 是咪垃圾黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/129187/page/10\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/129187/page/10</a>"}]}